{"tid":1295770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"防狗telegram group","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T07:40:31.000Z","uid":40324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92fdac7c5a5e54c7b8d6329575fb21bf5f0d50c1","tid":1295770,"uid":40324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到有巴打提出香港應該要打遊擊戰<br />\n[今後民意運動方針] [集思廣益] 今日我想同大家分享吓遊擊戰嘅概念<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1249686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1249686</a><br />\n<br />\n遊擊戰其中一個重點係要有足夠既溝通同聯絡<br />\n以「反送中」為主題既各種運動已經進行左一個月<br />\n呢一個月來都有好多group出現5毛同狗<br />\n導致好多資訊外洩/間唔中又忙住捉鬼<br />\n而我相信身邊邊啲係同路人都已經好清楚<br />\n會唔會可以開一個telegram group係只靠share link去邀請身邊人加入<br />\n以確保無鬼係個group<br />\n我地之後再進一步去討論遊擊/快閃活動?<br />\n純粹有個諗法 大家再討論下"},{"pid":"16b960b2e85766ddb28dfb55010a0c3d1384dac8","tid":1295770,"uid":29128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">只靠share link去邀請身邊人加入\n以確保無鬼係個group\n</code></pre><br />\n無可能"},{"pid":"c5ce3b8335aa023e33ec0a40dd73503a5fe84ccd","tid":1295770,"uid":40324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b960b2e85766ddb28dfb55010a0c3d1384dac8","tid":1295770,"uid":29128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">只靠share link去邀請身邊人加入\n以確保無鬼係個group\n</code></pre><br />\n無可能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"點解咁肯定呢?"},{"pid":"ceefaa98ea9e80eebc7c94550e6a0c5bbbd46b43","tid":1295770,"uid":32309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5ce3b8335aa023e33ec0a40dd73503a5fe84ccd","tid":1295770,"uid":40324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b960b2e85766ddb28dfb55010a0c3d1384dac8","tid":1295770,"uid":29128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">只靠share link去邀請身邊人加入\n以確保無鬼係個group\n</code></pre><br />\n無可能"},"cited